      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted (4.2 M, 11.7 M, 28.4 M cells). Richardson extrapolation applied; GCI on hemolysis index ranges 1.8%–3.4% across operating points. Asymptotic range confirmed. Discretization error level 4 achieved."
