      "rationale": "FDA experimental dataset specifies inlet profiles, temperature (37 °C ± 0.5 °C), and hematocrit (35% ± 2%). All boundary conditions are traceable to calibrated instruments. Deviations from nominal COU conditions are within ±3% and are propagated through UQ ensemble. Required level met."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
